<http://www.spektrix.com/gctc/event/118601ALPCMHJNQGBRCQPPCJSKTMSSSBV> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Lawyer Play 2026: Our Town";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">CCLA/GCTC Lawyer Play 2026:</span><span><br/></span><h2>Our Town</h2>by <span class=\"BoldText\">Thornton Wilder</span><span><br/></span>directed by <span class=\"BoldText\">Hugh Neilson</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>April 15 - 18, 2026<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Thornton Wilder’s beloved classic about everyday life, love, and the beauty we often miss while we’re busy living it.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guided by a charismatic Stage Manager, we’re welcomed into the world of Grover’s Corners to share in the lives of the Webb and Gibbs families. We, as the audience, watch their children grow up, fall in love, and start families of their own, while celebrating community, cherishing small moments, and reflecting on what truly matters.
""";
